title: Jimmy Osmond - Little Jimmy  1972
description:
This Has Got To Be The Worse Album I Have Ever Heard
How The Heck This Sold Over 70.000 Copys I Will Never Know

Whenever Peeps Comment On Your Singing - Stick This On

And Watch Their Reaction  Esspecially Track 02 - She Is Good Lookin&#039;

(He Sings It In Japanese)  Poor Lad .. At The Best Of Times He Had A Job Talking English... What With Them Teeth!!!

And No I Wasn&#039;t One Of The 70.000 Who Paid For The Album

It Was Left On My Doorstep By A Kind Old Lady Neighbour
Who I Can Tell You  Has Now Been Committed To Our Local
Mental Institution.... 
I Don&#039;t Know What Ward She&#039;s On ..But I think 
It&#039;s Next to ..The I Love Barry Manilow Ward

Best Of Luck

Windy
